---
---

<section id="about" class="bg-forest text-white">
  <!-- Editorial pull quote -->
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-5 py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-[auto_1fr] gap-8 md:gap-16 items-start">
      <!-- Vertical label -->
      <div class="hidden md:flex flex-col items-center gap-4 pt-2">
        <p class="text-white/30 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] rotate-180" style="writing-mode: vertical-rl">Est. 2012</p>
        <div class="w-px flex-1 bg-white/10 min-h-[120px]"></div>
      </div>

      <div>
        <blockquote class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold leading-tight text-white mb-8">
          "We've been in City Park West since 2012. We know the neighborhood — and we probably know your neighbor's dog."
        </blockquote>
        <p class="text-white/50 text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
          Not a chain. Not a franchise. Just a small grooming shop that's been part of this neighborhood for over a decade. We're not going anywhere.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap gap-8 pt-8 border-t border-white/10">
          <div>
            <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-gold">13+</p>
            <p class="text-white/50 text-sm mt-1">Years in Denver</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-gold">1-on-1</p>
            <p class="text-white/50 text-sm mt-1">Every appointment</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-gold">City Park West</p>
            <p class="text-white/50 text-sm mt-1">1438 E. 22nd Ave</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
